{
  "stem": "1160.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Digging, digging.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then he left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I went to the house, and one of the ladies-- I don't know which one, my mother or my aunt-- somebody told me I should go out to the end of the street.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They figured, because I'm the youngest, maybe nobody will look at me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I should go out to end of the Jewish street and wait there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe somebody will show up from the uncles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went a few times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they told me not to stay too long and come back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's what I did a few times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came back, and then I went back again, came back, went back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One time when I went back, I was lucky, because my-- this uncle, my mother's uncle, Herman Safar, he came.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I told him--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had been in the jail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He'd been in the jail.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They are all in the jail at this time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, everybody wants to know what's happening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they don't leave me alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're just sending me out here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So tell me what's happening.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he says, don't ask me questions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just go back and bring a glass of water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, yes, but come with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, no, just go and bring me a glass of water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, but I have to tell them what's going on, because they don't leave me alone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he says, just bring me the water.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I went back, and I said, the uncle wants a glass of water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was taking the water, and they told me, ask what's happening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I went back, I gave him the water, and he says, go home.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
